videos.description: Gonzaga's Rui Hachimura goes between the legs, then spins through a thicket of defenders for the wild lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hachimura breaks out sauce with filthy spin and score) 2019/2/9

videos.headline: Hachimura breaks out sauce with filthy spin and score

videos.description: Josh Perkins and Rui Hachimura cash in on an alley-oop pick-and-roll for the Zags' seventh consecutive make to begin the game.
videos.headline: Hachimura hammers alley-oop slam

videos.description: Josh Perkins whips a no-look pass to Brandon Clarke, who rises and throws down the and-1 flush for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Clarke smashes Perkins' no-look dime
